                                <p>Yes, GoToMyPC Android app gives you the flexibility to work on the go from your Android device or Kindle Fire so you can get anytime access to your files, programs, and network. You can connect to your Mac or PC using your Android phone or tablet, OS 4.5 or higher. If you don&rsquo;t see the app on Google Play and Amazon Appstore for Android, you may not be running Android 4.5 or higher, the minimum system requirement needed to install the app.</p>
<p>Note: To use this application, you must have a current GoToMyPC subscription. If you&rsquo;re not a subscriber, select the best plan for you on the <a href="/plansandpricing">plans and pricing page</a>.</p>
